--------------------------------------------------------------------------
DATA SOURCE ATTRIBUTIONS
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Golavo does not redistribute proprietary data. The open-core dataset is
built only from public-domain / open sources. Attribution requirements per
source (shown in-app on the screens that use them):

* openfootball (football.json)   — CC0-1.0 (public domain). No attribution
                                    required; credited voluntarily.
* martj42/international_results   — CC0-1.0 (public domain).
* Wikidata (structured data)      — CC0-1.0.
* Wyscout public event dataset    — CC BY 4.0. Cite: Pappalardo, L. et al.
  (Pappalardo et al., 2019)         "A public data set of spatio-temporal
                                    match events in soccer competitions."
                                    Scientific Data 6, 236 (2019).
* Open-Meteo (optional weather)   — Weather data CC BY 4.0. "Weather data by
                                    Open-Meteo.com". Free API is
                                    non-commercial use only.
* OpenLigaDB (optional overlay)   — Open Database License (ODbL) 1.0. Kept
                                    physically ISOLATED from CC0 data; its
                                    share-alike terms never contaminate the
                                    open-core warehouse. See docs: Legal.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
BYOK ADAPTERS (data stays on the user's machine; never redistributed)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Football-Data.org — when a user supplies their own key, the app displays
  the required attribution: "Football data provided by the Football-Data.org
  API". Data is not exported or redistributed and is purged when the key is
  removed.
* API-Football / api-sports.io — user-key only; data rendered in the
  key holder's private local session and never redistributed.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
EXCLUDED FROM THE PRODUCT
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
* StatsBomb Open Data is NOT bundled, redistributed, or used to train any
  shipped model weights. Its user agreement prohibits redistribution and
  commercial exploitation of derived analysis. Research use only, with the
  StatsBomb logo credited, outside this repository.

Golavo is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by FIFA, UEFA, any
league, club, or competition organizer. Competition names are used factually
(nominatively) to identify matches. No official logos, emblems, mascots,
trophy imagery, crests, or kit designs are used.
